{
  "stem": "26142.13",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Officially, it was supposed to be that you had to go through a physical examination.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "If you are not physically fit, then you are not good to, to, to go to war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But there was orders not to let down the lame, the, the, the, the deaf, the none, nobody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I remember when I, when I-- there were a bunch of doctors standing with tables in the middle of a soccer field, and soccer field, or whatever field it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was fenced around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And when they came, I, I said, I'm healthy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "No, you had to undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "You had to undress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And they counted up 200 or 220 and put you into a unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I fell into a unit that was called 104/108.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And, and at the same time, my brother Tsvi that was in, in, in, in Mariapocs already at that time, he also couldn't, couldn't stay there anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "He also had to get, to get in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And he, he got into a, to a-- his, his, I think, was [? 108/109. ?] And they organized those groups.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they-- we were sent out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We were sent out for training to a, a city near, you know, where Elie Wiesel was born in, in that city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sighetu.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next to that city was a small place, small place, [INAUDIBLE] something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed there for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, and then they loaded us up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they send us out behind the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They called it [INAUDIBLE], behind the Danube, into Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over there, they were building a, a international airport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, they didn't have bulldozers like now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had free slave laborers, Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
